                  </hi>. I am in the service of Mr. Walter, a pawnbroker, of Gos<lb></lb>well-street—I produce a coat, pawned by the prisoner on 7th June—she saidit was her husband's—there was a glove in the pocket—I produce a tea-pot, the person who took it in is not here.</p>
